\section{Loading one tutorial file}

Loading a tutorial file is the point where the textual format becomes the
typed runtime model.

<<functions>>=
def load_tutorial_file(path: str | Path) -> Tutorial:
    """Load one Markdown tutorial file into a [[Tutorial]]."""

    tutorial_path = Path(path).resolve()
    return parse_tutorial_text(
        tutorial_path.read_text(),
        source_path=tutorial_path,
    )
